    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/0f7e941f53b4e5847981401dd8798080.webp?t=1765903209\" width=498 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start as an ordinary cargo worker and gradually grow your cargo company by hiring new employees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/39572a9c62f5c92dbd69a8d119c0b592.poster.avif?t=1765903209\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/39572a9c62f5c92dbd69a8d119c0b592.webm?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/39572a9c62f5c92dbd69a8d119c0b592.mp4?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/3de49aadf9e81a924a37f8cfc22091ff.webp?t=1765903209\" width=498 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your office to be organized and efficient. Manage your cargo shelves and ensure a seamless experience for your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/01aa80b85a4730e4fd0fc7c47a96885c.poster.avif?t=1765903209\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/01aa80b85a4730e4fd0fc7c47a96885c.webm?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/01aa80b85a4730e4fd0fc7c47a96885c.mp4?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/bc12fc05b850e1078d987e27ebb85ed8.webp?t=1765903209\" width=498 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest your earnings into your company to grow. Expand your office, unlock new features to diversify your revenue streams, and automate processes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/18e3ac588d5dd332ff27ac4fa98b84fb.poster.avif?t=1765903209\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/18e3ac588d5dd332ff27ac4fa98b84fb.webm?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/18e3ac588d5dd332ff27ac4fa98b84fb.mp4?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/2d66f4729edffd4021e87bad34bc8867.webp?t=1765903209\" width=498 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set out for cargo delivery with your vehicle. Deliver to neighborhoods, the city, and drop-off points. If you prefer, you can also hire a courier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/14ca4b46eef79a155229e7611289732d.poster.avif?t=1765903209\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/14ca4b46eef79a155229e7611289732d.webm?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131690/extras/14ca4b46eef79a155229e7611289732d.mp4?t=1765903209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
